in the Power of humane Nature to conceal the
fir&s;t, or avoid the la&s;t.</P>
<P>What &s;hall I do? <HI>Amy,</HI> &s;aid I, <HI>as &s;oon as I cou'd
&s;peak;</HI> and what will become of me? and then I
