on all the Gravity upon her Countenance, that &s;he
was Mi&s;tre&s;s of; and that was not a little $word$.</P>
<P>When &s;he (<HI>the</HI> QUAKER) came into the Room,
(<HI>for they had &s;how'd my Daughter into a little Par|lour</HI>)
